text: To further confirm these results, we determined the neutralizing titer of immunized mouse sera (8/12, eight randomly selected samples from each group) against pH1N1 and PR8. Similar to HAI responses, neutralizing titers in sera was about 4-fold and 5-fold higher in mice immunized with AcHERV-VLP than in mice immunized with AcHERV-HA against pH1N1 virus and PR8 virus, respectively (Fig 3C) .
